{"tid":335851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[冇腦共狗] 藍絲爆粗高呼「隊冧長毛」 一女涉刑事恐嚇被捕","createTime":"2017-07-26T02:28:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T04:07:24.000Z","uid":77196,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ce4c757d36b37959c6f7b1485ec9c0825d901eb4","tid":335851,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T02:28:44.000Z","msg":"社民連前立法會議員梁國雄昨早前往政府總部抗議領展轉賣物業，途中遭多名親政府人士圍堵粗言辱罵，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>更出言恐嚇，「隊冧長毛」、「隊冧佢」，又指「馮敬恩（前港大學生會會長）都冇罪，大家都無罪」</strong></span>。梁報警求助，警方昨晚拘捕涉案一名65歲張姓婦人，涉嫌刑事恐嚇，案件交由中區警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n梁國雄表示，昨早應邀到政總出席抗議領展轉賣物業的記者會，但甫出港鐵站，在海富中心即被至少4名身穿「撐警」及印有國旗上衣的「藍絲」攔截指罵，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>更聲言「隊冧長毛」、「隊冧佢」，梁即場報警求助</strong></span>。根據梁提供的片段可見，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>其中一名戴黑框眼鏡的婦人稱，「馮敬恩話隊冧冇罪，我都跟住講」，「馮敬恩話冇罪個官，有罪我同馮敬恩一齊坐」</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n警員到場後嘗試調停，要求在場人士出示身份證登記，該名戴黑框眼鏡的婦人即向着梁國雄說，「有乜資格攞我身份證呀仆街」，「你而家仲係議員呀，你食屎啦仆街」。梁向在場警員表示遭推撞，該婦人即稱自己的腳也受傷；另一名「大媽」又呼叫「梁國雄打人」、「係咪想告？我哋攞片隊低佢」，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>又否認自己粗言恐嚇，「X家鏟係粗口嚟㗎咩」</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，昨早接報上址有爭執，經初步調查後，案件列作刑事恐嚇，一名65歲張姓女子被捕，現保釋候查，8月下旬向警方報到，案件交由中區警區刑事調查隊第8隊跟進。警方稱，處理及調查案件時，不論有關人士背景，均會按既定程序公平公正處理。"},{"pid":"2d828a6ad4aa74a2b3aadccc41485ff18cad051c","tid":335851,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T02:29:33.000Z","msg":"馮敬恩冇指明道姓話隊邊個，隻死共狗開到名都可以拉埋一齊講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e59b95689e27a6b693193d484a77e5a8cf50629","tid":335851,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T02:37:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff61c4f6f6c4021b549bc26889f217dfb8801fc3","tid":335851,"uid":101390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T02:41:22.000Z","msg":"又一隻死廢老亂吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ffa2f585ce24278797e1f6d6248e25b4dd5b0a1","tid":335851,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T03:14:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15390ee0f7f2ee2538bd24e90d653e44a2067344","tid":335851,"uid":12565,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T03:34:59.000Z","msg":"係呀係呀講多啲啦<br />\nBilly 刑恐就告唔入嘅<br />\n你哋多啲藍絲狗一齊講到明係「隊冧長毛」就隨時刑恐罪成一車車送入去坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b467ad0d89cedd0a689faf78a2325f80abe2fc3d","tid":335851,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T03:36:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係呀係呀講多啲啦<br />\nBilly 刑恐就告唔入嘅<br />\n你哋多啲藍絲狗一齊講到明係「隊冧長毛」就隨時刑恐罪成一車車送入去坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但班on9藍絲唔記得Billy仲有另一條罪告得入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd55cd9b90e8c1872f7840366b8af5655fdef6d","tid":335851,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T03:44:17.000Z","msg":"馮敬恩刑恐唔入但另外3條入呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d62cdeb38874ce942e599bd85b050cc765abdfe3","tid":335851,"uid":12565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T03:44:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係呀係呀講多啲啦<br />\nBilly 刑恐就告唔入嘅<br />\n你哋多啲藍絲狗一齊講到明係「隊冧長毛」就隨時刑恐罪成一車車送入去坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但班on9藍絲唔記得Billy仲有另一條罪告得入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBilly 刑恐告唔入係因為佢冇講明係隊冧李國章<br />\n但講「隊冧佢」第二條輕啲嘅都係入咗（好似係擾亂秩序罪）<br />\n而家班大媽就算兜到唔係「長毛」唔係指梁國雄（其實都幾難兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n點都中「擾亂秩序罪」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff4fc4ee607ea5145a8dd2d6ca56ca70cc05add9","tid":335851,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T03:45:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係呀係呀講多啲啦<br />\nBilly 刑恐就告唔入嘅<br />\n你哋多啲藍絲狗一齊講到明係「隊冧長毛」就隨時刑恐罪成一車車送入去坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但班on9藍絲唔記得Billy仲有另一條罪告得入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBilly 刑恐告唔入係因為佢冇講明係隊冧李國章<br />\n但講「隊冧佢」第二條輕啲嘅都係入咗（好似係擾亂秩序罪）<br />\n而家班大媽就算兜到唔係「長毛」唔係指梁國雄（其實都幾難兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n點都中「擾亂秩序罪」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係落案起訴佢先講"},{"pid":"3c38230eb503179c2c421ae57898f234fde5228a","tid":335851,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T03:47:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>馮敬恩刑恐唔入但另外3條入呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有兩條係認罪"},{"pid":"02f7f1f6ad7d3084fa05b14ed344b62814284cd7","tid":335851,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:33:14.000Z","msg":"低質藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81e9098eeb17782de71385dbc1abadb6399fa3f","tid":335851,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T13:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa1de72d846b5eb9a045b59543ea01ea67a3562","tid":335851,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:07:24.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}